{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"58a441b6da","title":"对中央关于国庆节挂像、抬像办法和口号的通知稿的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0e4f48e67d","index":0,"year":1966,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"58a441b6da"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dbcf15bd08","name":"陶铸","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"accfd48623","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陶铸，当时任中共中央政治局常委、中央书记处常务书记、中央文化革命小组顾问、中央宣传部部长。"},{"id":"acdb62bdfd","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在陶铸1966年9月10日送审的中共中央关于1966年国庆节挂像、拾像办法和标语、口号的通知稿上。通知稿除提出国庆节挂像、拾像的三条规定外，还列举了标语60条、口号40条，共100条。毛泽东在审阅时，对标语作了大量的删减。"},{"id":"cf1809dd08","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在陶铸1966年9月11日送审的通知修改稿上，修改后的标语与口号合在一起，共30条。"},{"id":"f2079b492d","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林彪，在中共八届十一中全会上继续当选为中央政治局常委，不久被称中央副主席。"},{"id":"3383074ffe","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陶，指陶铸。周，指周恩来。任重，即王任重，当时任中共中央文化革命小组副组长、中南局第一书记。"},{"id":"6c1022bb3a","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da","index":6,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在陶铸1966年9月14日送审的通知修改稿上。陶铸在送审报告中写道：“遵示送文革小组讨论，又修改了一次，特再送陈审阅。这次修改稿的标题改为《关于一九六六年国庆节挂像、拾像办法和口号的通知》，其中口号被压缩为23条。"},{"id":"8f4548f157","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da","index":7,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在陶铸1966年9月15日晨2时送审的通知修改稿上。这次送审稿对23条口号又作了个别内容上的修改。"},{"id":"57dcb80805","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da","index":8,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在陶铸1966年9月16日送审的通知修改稿上。这次送审稿上加了“鼓足干劲，力争上游，多快好省地建设社会主义”和“巩固无产阶级专政！加强工农联盟”两条口号，最后定稿为25条。9月17日，中共中央将这一通知下发到县团级。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c378b35ba8","type":"title","text":"对中央关于国庆节挂像、拾像办法和口号的通知稳的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"accfd48623","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"acdb62bdfd","type":"paragraph","text":"标语、口号太多，是烦项哲学，要大精简，各有十几条就够了，至多总共不要超过三十条。多了，谁也不记得，不看作一回事了。请再议削，印出交来。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"cf1809dd08","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"f2079b492d","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十日陶铸同志","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"3383074ffe","type":"paragraph","text":"省得多了，不知送中央文革小组讨论过没有？如未，请送他们议一下。m","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"6c1022bb3a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"8f4548f157","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十二日","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"57dcb80805","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"7124b24747","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪同志阅后退陶铸同志照办。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"5e620423d6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"39f3dfa67e","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十四日下午","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"b3c06d8c19","type":"paragraph","text":"凡事要思索，不宜仓碎作出决定。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"d994396ac3","type":"paragraph","text":"凡大事要征求较多同志的意见。请陶、周、任重\"注意。标语、口号由100条改为23条，较好，是一教训。毛又及”","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"d77b8bea01","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"566050c3a5","type":"paragraph","text":"同意。以","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"},{"id":"482c95ef19","type":"subtitle","text":"五同意。H","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da"}],"page":{"id":"83fae5e682","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58a441b6da","start":67,"end":69}}}},"__N_SSG":true}